'''The Equestrian Events at the [[1924 Summer Olympics|1924 Paris Olympics]]''' included [[Eventing]] (individual and team medals), [[Show Jumping]] (team medals) and [[Dressage]] (individual medals). All three disciplines had both individual and team competitions. Vaulting was not included this year.

